\end_inset

 es su vector tangente, [...] 
\begin_inset Formula $\kappa(s):=|\mathbf{t}'(s)|$
\end_inset

.
 [...] 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{n}(s):=\frac{\mathbf{t}'(s)}{\kappa(s)}[...],$
