[...] 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{b}(s)=\mathbf{t}(s)\land\mathbf{n}(s)$
\end_inset

 [...].
 [...] 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau(s)[...]=\langle\mathbf{b}'(s),\mathbf{n}(s)\rangle$
\end_inset

.
 [...]
