X_{uv} & =\Gamma_{12}^{1}X_{u}+\Gamma_{12}^{2}X_{v}+fN,\\
X_{vu} & =\Gamma_{21}^{1}X_{u}+\Gamma_{21}^{2}X_{v}+fN,\\
X_{vv} & =\Gamma_{22}^{1}X_{u}+\Gamma_{22}^{2}X_{v}+gN
\end{aligned}
\right.
\]

\end_inset

donde los 
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma_{ij}^{k}$
\end_inset

 son los 
\series bold
símbolos de Christoffel
